{"word":"μοιχάω","slug":"μοιχάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μοιχάω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μοιχός\">μοιχός</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> ‘be put into an adulterous state or condition’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of a woman, in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b>commit adultery <a href='B:480 10:12'>Mk 10:12</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of a man, in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> sense <b>commit adultery <a href='B:470 5:32'>Mt 5:32</a>; <a href='B:470 19:9'>19:9</a></b> and as<b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> elsewhere in the same <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vs.\">vs.</a>; <b><a href='B:480 10:11'>Mk 10:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μοιχαλίς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:μοιχεία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}